#. <section class="sutta" id="sn12.31"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn12.31:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 12"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 12"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.31:0.2"
msgid "4. Kaḷārakhattiyavagga"
msgstr "4. Kaḷāra the Aristocrat"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn12.31:0.3"
msgid "31. Bhūtasutta"
msgstr "31. What Has Come to Be"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.31:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn12.31:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr "Then the Buddha said to Venerable Sāriputta:"

#. VAR: pārāyane → pārāyaṇe (bj) | parāyane (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn12.31:1.3"
msgid "“vuttamidaṃ, sāriputta, pārāyane ajitapañhe:"
msgstr ""
"“Sāriputta, this was said in ‘The Way to the Beyond’, in ‘The Questions of "
"Ajita’:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.31:2.1"
msgid "‘Ye ca saṅkhātadhammāse,"
msgstr "‘Those who have comprehended the teaching,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:2.2"
msgid "ye ca sekkhā puthū idha;"
msgstr "and the many kinds of trainees here—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:2.3"
msgid "Tesaṃ me nipako iriyaṃ,"
msgstr "dear sir, you are self-disciplined;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:2.4"
msgid "puṭṭho pabrūhi mārisā’ti."
msgstr "when questioned, please tell me their conduct.’"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.31:3.1"
msgid ""
"Imassa nu kho, sāriputta, saṅkhittena bhāsitassa kathaṃ vitthārena attho "
"daṭṭhabbo”ti?"
msgstr "How should we see the detailed meaning of this brief statement?”"

msgctxt "sn12.31:3.2"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā sāriputto tuṇhī ahosi."
msgstr "When he said this, Sāriputta kept silent."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.31:4.1"
msgid "Dutiyampi kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ āmantesi … pe …"
msgstr "For a second time …"

msgctxt "sn12.31:4.2"
msgid "dutiyampi kho āyasmā sāriputto tuṇhī ahosi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.31:4.3"
msgid "Tatiyampi kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr "and a third time …"

msgctxt "sn12.31:4.4"
msgid "“vuttamidaṃ, sāriputta, pārāyane ajitapañhe:"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.31:5.1"
msgid "‘Ye ca saṅkhātadhammāse,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:5.2"
msgid "ye ca sekkhā puthū idha;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:5.3"
msgid "Tesaṃ me nipako iriyaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:5.4"
msgid "puṭṭho pabrūhi mārisā’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.48"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.31:6.1"
msgid ""
"Imassa nu kho, sāriputta, saṅkhittena bhāsitassa kathaṃ vitthārena attho "
"daṭṭhabbo”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.31:6.2"
msgid "Tatiyampi kho āyasmā sāriputto tuṇhī ahosi."
msgstr "Sāriputta kept silent."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.31:7.1"
msgid "“Bhūtamidanti, sāriputta, passasī”ti?"
msgstr "“Sāriputta, do you see that this has come to be?”"

msgctxt "sn12.31:7.2"
msgid "“Bhūtamidanti, bhante, yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati."
msgstr "“Sir, one truly sees with right wisdom that this has come to be."

msgctxt "sn12.31:7.3"
msgid ""
"Bhūtamidanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā bhūtassa nibbidāya virāgāya "
"nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti."
msgstr ""
"Seeing this, one is practicing for disillusionment, dispassion, and "
"cessation regarding what has come to be."

msgctxt "sn12.31:7.4"
msgid "Tadāhārasambhavanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati."
msgstr "One truly sees with right wisdom that it originated with that as fuel."

msgctxt "sn12.31:7.5"
msgid ""
"Tadāhārasambhavanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā āhārasambhavassa "
"nibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti."
msgstr ""
"Seeing this, one is practicing for disillusionment, dispassion, and "
"cessation regarding the fuel for its origination."

msgctxt "sn12.31:7.6"
msgid ""
"Tadāhāranirodhā yaṃ bhūtaṃ taṃ nirodhadhammanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya "
"passati."
msgstr ""
"One truly sees with right wisdom that when that fuel ceases, what has come "
"to be is liable to cease."

msgctxt "sn12.31:7.7"
msgid ""
"Tadāhāranirodhā yaṃ bhūtaṃ taṃ nirodhadhammanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya "
"disvā nirodhadhammassa nibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti."
msgstr ""
"Seeing this, one is practicing for disillusionment, dispassion, and "
"cessation regarding what is liable to cease."

msgctxt "sn12.31:7.8"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhante, sekkho hoti."
msgstr "In this way one is a trainee."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.49"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.31:8.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhante, saṅkhātadhammo hoti?"
msgstr "And what, sir, is one who has comprehended the teaching?"

msgctxt "sn12.31:8.2"
msgid "Bhūtamidanti, bhante, yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati."
msgstr "Sir, one truly sees with right wisdom that this has come to be."

msgctxt "sn12.31:8.3"
msgid ""
"Bhūtamidanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā bhūtassa nibbidā virāgā nirodhā "
"anupādā vimutto hoti."
msgstr ""
"Seeing this, one is freed by not grasping through disillusionment, "
"dispassion, and cessation regarding what has come to be."

msgctxt "sn12.31:8.4"
msgid "Tadāhārasambhavanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati."
msgstr "One truly sees with right wisdom that it originated with that as fuel."

msgctxt "sn12.31:8.5"
msgid ""
"Tadāhārasambhavanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā āhārasambhavassa nibbidā "
"virāgā nirodhā anupādā vimutto hoti."
msgstr ""
"Seeing this, one is freed by not grasping through disillusionment, "
"dispassion, and cessation regarding the fuel for its origination."

msgctxt "sn12.31:8.6"
msgid ""
"Tadāhāranirodhā yaṃ bhūtaṃ taṃ nirodhadhammanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya "
"passati."
msgstr ""
"One truly sees with right wisdom that when that fuel ceases, what has come "
"to be is liable to cease."

msgctxt "sn12.31:8.7"
msgid ""
"Tadāhāranirodhā yaṃ bhūtaṃ taṃ nirodhadhammanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya "
"disvā nirodhadhammassa nibbidā virāgā nirodhā anupādā vimutto hoti."
msgstr ""
"Seeing this, one is freed by not grasping through disillusionment, "
"dispassion, and cessation regarding what is liable to cease."

msgctxt "sn12.31:8.8"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhante, saṅkhātadhammo hoti."
msgstr "In this way one has comprehended the teaching."

msgctxt "sn12.31:8.9"
msgid "Iti kho, bhante, yaṃ taṃ vuttaṃ pārāyane ajitapañhe:"
msgstr ""
"Sir, regarding what was said in ‘The Way to the Beyond’, in ‘The Questions "
"of Ajita’:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.31:9.1"
msgid "‘Ye ca saṅkhātadhammāse,"
msgstr "‘Those who have comprehended the teaching,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:9.2"
msgid "ye ca sekkhā puthū idha;"
msgstr "and the many kinds of trainees here—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:9.3"
msgid "Tesaṃ me nipako iriyaṃ,"
msgstr "dear sir, you are self-disciplined;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:9.4"
msgid "puṭṭho pabrūhi mārisā’ti."
msgstr "when questioned, please tell me their conduct.’"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.31:10.1"
msgid ""
"Imassa khvāhaṃ, bhante, saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ vitthārena atthaṃ "
"ājānāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is how I understand the detailed meaning of what was said in brief.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.31:11.1"
msgid ""
"“Sādhu sādhu, sāriputta, bhūtamidanti, sāriputta, yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya "
"passati."
msgstr ""
"“Good, good, Sāriputta!” (The Buddha repeated all of Sāriputta’s "
"explanation, concluding:)"

msgctxt "sn12.31:11.2"
msgid ""
"Bhūtamidanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā bhūtassa nibbidāya virāgāya "
"nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.31:11.3"
msgid "Tadāhārasambhavanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.31:11.4"
msgid ""
"Tadāhārasambhavanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā āhārasambhavassa "
"nibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.31:11.5"
msgid ""
"Tadāhāranirodhā yaṃ bhūtaṃ taṃ nirodhadhammanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya "
"passati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.31:11.6"
msgid ""
"Tadāhāranirodhā yaṃ bhūtaṃ taṃ nirodhadhammanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya "
"disvā nirodhadhammassa nibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.31:11.7"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, sāriputta, sekkho hoti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.50"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.31:12.1"
msgid "Kathañca, sāriputta, saṅkhātadhammo hoti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.31:12.2"
msgid "Bhūtamidanti, sāriputta, yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.31:12.3"
msgid ""
"Bhūtamidanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā bhūtassa nibbidā virāgā nirodhā "
"anupādā vimutto hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.31:12.4"
msgid "Tadāhārasambhavanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.31:12.5"
msgid ""
"Tadāhārasambhavanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā āhārasambhavassa nibbidā "
"virāgā nirodhā anupādā vimutto hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.31:12.6"
msgid ""
"Tadāhāranirodhā yaṃ bhūtaṃ taṃ nirodhadhammanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya "
"passati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.31:12.7"
msgid ""
"Tadāhāranirodhā yaṃ bhūtaṃ taṃ nirodhadhammanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññā "
"disvā nirodhadhammassa nibbidā virāgā nirodhā anupādā vimutto hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.31:12.8"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, sāriputta, saṅkhātadhammo hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.31:12.9"
msgid "Iti kho, sāriputta, yaṃ taṃ vuttaṃ pārāyane ajitapañhe:"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.31:13.1"
msgid "‘Ye ca saṅkhātadhammāse,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:13.2"
msgid "ye ca sekkhā puthū idha;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:13.3"
msgid "Tesaṃ me nipako iriyaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:13.4"
msgid "puṭṭho pabrūhi mārisā’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.31:14.1"
msgid ""
"Imassa kho, sāriputta, saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ vitthārena attho "
"daṭṭhabbo”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is how to understand the detailed meaning of what was said in brief.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.31:14.2"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
